# ğŸ› ï¸ **How to Build & Run**

This project includes a **Makefile**, allowing users to build and run with just a few commands.

## âœ… 1. Clone the Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/DonohoM/Hell-s-Managment-System.git
```

## âœ… 2. Navigate Into the Source Directory

```bash
cd Hell-s-Managment-System/CS\(221\)Project_1
```

## âœ… 3. Build the Program

```bash
make
```

This produces an executable called:

```
hell_management
```

## â–¶ï¸ 4. Run the Program

```bash
./hell_management
```

## ğŸ§¹ 5. Clean Build Files

```bash
make clean
```

